Intent Traceability Law (Cursor compatibility file)

Primary rule source:
- .cursor/rules/intent-traceability-law.mdc

Mandatory policy summary:
1. Select active intent before any mutating action.
2. Enforce owned_scope for all file mutations.
3. Append trace records to .orchestration/agent_trace.jsonl for each successful mutation.
4. Keep pre-hooks fail-closed and post-hooks fail-safe.
5. Do not bypass governance checks.
